FBIS4-26921 "drchi124_m_94002" FBIS-CHI-94-124 Daily Report 25 Jun 1994 Military Shandong Commander Attends Militia Work Conference Shandong Commander Attends Militia Work Conference SK2606033494 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network in Mandarin 2300 GMT 25 Jun 94 SK2606033494 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network Mandarin BFN [Text] On 25 June in Linyi, the provincial government and the provincial military district cosponsored a work conference on construction and management of militia equipment, warehouses, and (?arms repair centers). Yi Yuanqiu, commander of the provincial military district, pointed out at the conference: At present and in the foreseeable future, we should achieve the development and readjustment of militia arms and equipment; ceaselessly upgrade their technological guaranteeing capability; realistically strengthen the safety in their management; make the militia arms and equipment attain, on a step-by-step basis, the goals of higher quality, reasonable distribution, good technology, and safety in storage; and enhance the militiamen's ability in supporting the Army's operations and shouldering the task of safeguarding social order.
